Bug #2: database.php - Destructor Error ✅ FIXED
File: config/database.php (line 219-223)

Problem:

// BROKEN - No instance check
public function close() {
    if ($this->conn) {
        $this->conn->close(); // Error!
    }
}
Fix:

// FIXED - Added instanceof check
public function close() {
    if ($this->conn && $this->conn instanceof mysqli) {
        $this->conn->close();
        $this->conn = null; // Prevent reuse
    }
}
Impact:

❌ Error: "mysqli::close(): Couldn't fetch mysqli"
❌ Connection tidak tertutup dengan benar
❌ Potential memory leaks
Status: ✅ FIXED

